headline: Vinson & Elkins Advises Coterra Energy on Power Purchase Agreement with PROPWR
summary: By Exec Edge Editorial Staff Vinson & Elkins advised Coterra Energy Inc. on a behind-the-meter power purchase agreement with PROPWR, a subsidiary of ProPetro Holding Corp., to develop a distributed microgrid at Coterra’s production sites in the New Mexico portion of the Permian Basin. The Vinson & Elkins team was led by partner Mark Brasher […]
